dcterms:description: The PaSC database contains still-to-still and video-to-video matching protocols. The frontal subset of the still-to-still protocol includes 4,688 images pertaining to 293 individuals, divided into equal size target and query sets.
dcterms:title: PaSC

dcterms:description: The MEDS-II database contains a total of 1,309 faces pertaining to 518 individuals. A subset of 858 frontal face images is utilized for matching, with each image matched to every other image.
dcterms:title: MEDS-II
